  "description": "<h1>Tromsø</h1>\n<h3>TOS · 1.0.0</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Subway-Builder-Modded/registry/refs/heads/main/maps/tromso-no/gallery/screenshot1.webp\" alt=\"Map Preview\"></p>\n<h2>Coverage</h2>\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Bounding box</strong></td><td>18.59007, 69.42508, 19.56431, 69.80329</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Playable Area</strong></td><td>1586 km²</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Population Summary</h2>\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Total Modeled Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">79,068</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Modeled Normal Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">55,013</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Modeled Special Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">24,055</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Map Statistics</h2>\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Demand Points</strong></td><td align=\"right\">695</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Populations</strong></td><td align=\"right\">2479</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Special Demand</h2>\n<details>\n<summary>Airports — 2800</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;TOS&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;2800&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Universities — 12,000</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;University of Tromsø&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;12,000&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Entertainment — 9180</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Polarmuseet&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;250&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Tromsø Arktisk-Alpine Botanisk Hage&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;175&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Norges Arktiske Universitetsmuseum&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;200&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Ishavskatedralen&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;425&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Polaria&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;875&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Troll Museum&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;125&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Tromsø Domkirke&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;225&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Telegrafbukta&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;425&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Templarheimen Idrettspark/Tromsø Klatresenter/Tromsøbadet&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;825&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Perspektivet Museum&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;75&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Nordnorsk Vitensenter&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;150&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;MS Polstjerna&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;70&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Roald Amundsen Monument&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;550&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Jekta Storsenter&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;3600&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Prestvannet&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;275&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Nordnorsk Kunstmuseum&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;90&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Fjellheisen&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;550&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Vår Frue Domkirke i Tromsø&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;70&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Tromsø Alpinpark&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;275&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Skansen Festningsverk&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;550&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Military Bases — 75</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Olavsvern&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;75&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n<br>\n\n<h2>Additional Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Building Collision</strong> — A buildings index is included, providing in-game collision geometry for all non-filtered buildings.</li>\n<li><strong>Neighborhood Labels</strong> — The map includes municipal and neighborhood labels derived from administrative boundary data.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Methodology</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Processed 250m x 250m country data for the bounding box.</li>\n<li>Applied a modified version of Colin&#39;s gravity model to generate commutes.</li>\n<li>Special demand added using the Demand Adder.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Data Sources</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://kartkatalog.geonorge.no/Metadata/bedrifter-pa-rutenett/7dcf4a32-b150-48f6-bae6-f8a25fab300c\">Statistisk sentralbyrå Bedrifter 250m 2026</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://kartkatalog.geonorge.no/Metadata/0c0ad0ce-55e8-4d73-9c12-0eb0e2454acb\">Statistisk sentralbyrå Befolkning 250m 2026</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>License</h2>\n<p>This map data is released under the <a href=\"https://github.com/rslurry/subwaybuilder-maps/blob/main/LICENSE\">GNU General Public License v3.0</a>.</p>\n<h2>Credits</h2>\n<p>Map authored by slurry</p>",
